	heroSubhead={`The weight is real — the long hours, the lives in your hands, the moment you couldn't save someone, the unspoken rule that you have to be the strong one. Here's the truth underneath the white coat: you have a Father in heaven who carries the One who carries everyone, so you can practice from rest instead of the impossible weight of being everything.`}
