	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for doctors`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a rulebook`, bodyHtml: `Most Bibles can read like one more set of expectations — the last thing an exhausted physician needs. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of another authority telling you to perform, you meet the One who already delights in you.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, with audio — between rounds or on the commute`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen between rounds, on the drive home, or in the quiet after a hard shift. The Father's voice fits into the few minutes your day actually has.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to the weight you carry`, bodyHtml: `Exhausted? Numb? Carrying a loss you can't put down? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to bring it to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where the work has left you.` },
